  "detailed_description": "<h1>Alchemist Shop Simulator - run your magic business! - DEMO available now!</h1><p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PLAY the Demo, please WISHLIST the full game!</h2></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/501120/extras/a700bf72f70c80864775c5e3d157bb4b.avif?t=1751031143\" width=620 height=83 /></span><br>Experience time from an entirely new perspective, whether you're looking for a challenge, some relaxation, or just a bit of fun. The only task required of a clock is to tick forward every second. Over and over, second by second. Sounds easy, right? But could YOU handle it? Take a deep breath. Unwind. Tap into your inner rhythm. Click once every second. Consistently. Become the clock.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/501120/extras/f8b311455443f7b3b571c538bf3c5f61.poster.avif?t=1751031143\" width=620 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/501120/extras/f8b311455443f7b3b571c538bf3c5f61.webm?t=1751031143\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/501120/extras/f8b311455443f7b3b571c538bf3c5f61.mp4?t=1751031143\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Get Clock Simulator and...</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Discover a novel take on rhythm gaming distilled to one simple idea: become the clock<br></li><li>Enjoy intuitive controls so simple you could play with your eyes closed (maybe you should!)<br></li><li>Challenge yourself at the very basic, innermost level of your very own heartbeat<br></li><li>Master a diverse selection of modes and themes, from the calming to the competitive<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/501120/extras/8bcca3f72c3135d077e9e2671b4df5a9.avif?t=1751031143\" width=620 height=83 /></span><br></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/501120/extras/a700bf72f70c80864775c5e3d157bb4b.avif?t=1751031143\" width=620 height=83 /></span><br>Experience time from an entirely new perspective, whether you're looking for a challenge, some relaxation, or just a bit of fun. The only task required of a clock is to tick forward every second. Over and over, second by second. Sounds easy, right? But could YOU handle it? Take a deep breath. Unwind. Tap into your inner rhythm. Click once every second. Consistently. Become the clock.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/501120/extras/f8b311455443f7b3b571c538bf3c5f61.poster.avif?t=1751031143\" width=620 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/501120/extras/f8b311455443f7b3b571c538bf3c5f61.webm?t=1751031143\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/501120/extras/f8b311455443f7b3b571c538bf3c5f61.mp4?t=1751031143\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Get Clock Simulator and...</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Discover a novel take on rhythm gaming distilled to one simple idea: become the clock<br></li><li>Enjoy intuitive controls so simple you could play with your eyes closed (maybe you should!)<br></li><li>Challenge yourself at the very basic, innermost level of your very own heartbeat<br></li><li>Master a diverse selection of modes and themes, from the calming to the competitive<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/501120/extras/8bcca3f72c3135d077e9e2671b4df5a9.avif?t=1751031143\" width=620 height=83 /></span><br></li></ul>",
